# Assets Directory

Static assets for the shoa-site project.

## Directory Structure

```
assets/
├── images/          # All images
│   ├── avatar/      # Profile pictures
│   ├── blog/        # Blog post images (by date: YYYY/MM/)
│   └── projects/    # Project screenshots
├── fonts/           # Custom fonts (if any)
└── downloads/       # Downloadable files
```

## Quick Reference

### Blog Image Path Formula
```
Local:   assets/images/blog/YYYY/MM/filename.jpg
CDN:     https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/shoa-lin/shoa-site@main/assets/images/blog/YYYY/MM/filename.jpg
```

### Example
```markdown
Blog: assets/images/blog/2025/12/my-post-cover.jpg
CDN:  https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/shoa-lin/shoa-site@main/assets/images/blog/2025/12/my-post-cover.jpg
```
